<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="nav-container">
                <div class="logo">
                    <h1>Edgeview Finance</h1>
                    <span>Business Solutions</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="nav-menu">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/equipment-finance">Equipment Finance</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/working-capital">Working Capital</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Expert Consultation</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section - North Lakes Specific -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Commercial Finance Solutions for North Lakes Growth Corridor Businesses</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    Strategic equipment finance, commercial property loans, and working capital solutions designed for North Lakes commercial trades and logistics businesses. 
                    Professional assessment and expert guidance for sustainable growth in Brisbane's premier northern development corridor.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-cta">
                    <a href="/get-quote" class="primary-button">Get Professional Assessment</a>
                    <a href="/calculator" class="secondary-button">Calculate Repayments</a>
                </div>
                <div class="trust-indicators">
                    <span>✓ Licensed Australian Finance Broker</span>
                    <span>✓ ASIC Compliant Service</span>
                    <span>✓ North Lakes Growth Corridor Specialists</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- North Lakes Market Overview -->
        <section class="market-overview">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Understanding North Lakes' Commercial Finance Landscape</h2>
                <div class="market-content">
                    <p>
                        North Lakes represents Brisbane's most dynamic northern growth corridor, strategically positioned between the CBD and Sunshine Coast. 
                        With major residential developments, expanding industrial estates, and excellent transport connectivity via Bruce Highway and rail links, this region offers exceptional opportunities for commercial trades, logistics operators, and service businesses positioned to leverage strategic finance solutions.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="market-insights">
                        <div class="insight-card">
                            <h3>Growth Corridor Dynamics</h3>
                            <p>North Lakes and surrounding areas like Mango Hill and Griffin are experiencing unprecedented growth, driving demand for specialized equipment, facility development, and working capital solutions across construction, logistics, and commercial service sectors.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="insight-card">
                            <h3>Transport Infrastructure Advantage</h3>
                            <p>Strategic position on Bruce Highway with upcoming rail connectivity provides exceptional access to Brisbane CBD, Sunshine Coast, and northern markets, enabling business expansion with appropriate finance support.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="insight-card">
                            <h3>Industrial Development Boom</h3>
                            <p>New industrial estates and business parks create consistent opportunities for commercial trades, logistics operators, and specialized service businesses to establish or expand operations in this high-growth region.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- North Lakes Services Overview -->
        <section class="services-overview">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Commercial Finance Services for North Lakes Businesses</h2>
                <div class="services-grid">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h3>North Lakes Equipment Finance</h3>
                        <p>Strategic equipment financing for North Lakes commercial trades, logistics operators, and industrial businesses. Competitive rates from $20K to $500K+ with flexible terms designed for Queensland's northern growth corridor economy.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Construction and earthmoving equipment for new developments</li>
                            <li>Logistics and freight handling equipment</li>
                            <li>Commercial vehicles for corridor operations</li>
                            <li>Specialized trade machinery for growth markets</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/equipment-finance">Explore Equipment Finance →</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h3>North Lakes Commercial Property Finance</h3>
                        <p>Professional property finance for North Lakes business premises acquisition or investment opportunities. Navigate the dynamic growth corridor property market with strategic structuring and expert guidance.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Industrial properties in new business parks</li>
                            <li>Commercial premises in growth corridors</li>
                            <li>Warehouse and logistics facilities</li>
                            <li>Mixed-use commercial developments</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/commercial-property">Explore Property Finance →</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h3>North Lakes Working Capital Solutions</h3>
                        <p>Strategic working capital and cash flow management designed for North Lakes commercial trades and logistics businesses. Support rapid growth initiatives and manage cash flow during expansion phases.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Growth capital for expanding operations</li>
                            <li>Invoice factoring for commercial contracts</li>
                            <li>Business credit facilities for development projects</li>
                            <li>Project funding for infrastructure contracts</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/working-capital">Explore Working Capital →</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- North Lakes Service Areas -->
        <section class="service-areas">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>North Lakes & Northern Growth Corridor Areas We Serve</h2>
                <p>Edgeview Finance Business Solutions provides strategic commercial finance services across North Lakes and the broader northern Brisbane growth corridor:</p>
                
                <div class="areas-grid">
                    {locationData.serviceAreas.map(area => (
                        <div class="area-card">
                            <h4>{area}</h4>
                            <p>Commercial finance services for trades and service businesses</p>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
                
                <div class="areas-detail">
                    <h3>Comprehensive Northern Corridor Coverage</h3>
                    <p>
                        From North Lakes' expanding business districts to established industrial areas in Brendale and emerging developments in Aura, we understand the unique dynamics of each location. 
                        Our strategic finance solutions are tailored to the specific opportunities and challenges faced by businesses across this rapidly developing northern corridor.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- North Lakes Success Stories -->
        <section class="success-stories">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>North Lakes Business Success Stories</h2>
                <div class="stories-grid">
                    <div class="story-card">
                        <h3>Mango Hill Logistics Business</h3>
                        <p>Secured $420K equipment finance for warehouse expansion and delivery fleet upgrade. Strategic structuring enabled rapid scaling to service Brisbane-Sunshine Coast corridor demand during the area's residential boom.</p>
                        <span class="story-outcome">Result: 85% increase in delivery capacity within 8 months</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="story-card">
                        <h3>North Lakes Commercial Contractor</h3>
                        <p>$380K working capital facility provided cash flow stability during major residential development projects. Professional assessment identified optimal structure for rapid growth revenue patterns.</p>
                        <span class="story-outcome">Result: Secured four major subdivision development contracts</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="story-card">
                        <h3>Griffin Industrial Business</h3>
                        <p>$550K commercial property finance enabled strategic facility acquisition in prime growth corridor location. Finance structure created equity position and operational efficiency advantages.</p>
                        <span class="story-outcome">Result: 40% reduction in operational costs and strategic market expansion</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Choose EVFBS for North Lakes -->
        <section class="why-choose">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Why North Lakes Businesses Choose EVFBS</h2>
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Growth Corridor Expertise</h3>
                        <p>Deep understanding of North Lakes' unique position as Brisbane's premier northern growth corridor. We know the opportunities facing businesses in this dynamic development zone.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Northern Corridor Specialization</h3>
                        <p>Focus on commercial trades, logistics operators, and industrial businesses that leverage the strategic northern corridor position. Excluding residential building to concentrate on sustainable commercial sectors.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>Strategic Partnership Approach</h3>
                        <p>Professional assessment process ensures finance solutions align with North Lakes business goals and regional growth opportunities. Transparent guidance throughout the entire process.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h3>AI-Enhanced Growth Intelligence</h3>
                        <p>Advanced analytics provide insights into North Lakes market conditions, development patterns, and cash flow forecasting specific to your business sector and growth corridor location.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Access Strategic Commercial Finance in North Lakes?</h2>
                <p>Join hundreds of northern corridor business builders who've secured strategic finance solutions through our professional partnership approach.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/get-quote" class="primary-button large">Request Professional Assessment</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="secondary-button large">Speak with a North Lakes Finance Specialist</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>Edgeview Finance Business Solutions</h4>
